                    | Any prime occurring in this must also occur in #[m h_{D_k}(P)] for some #[m k] (except for a finite set #[m \{p : p|f \text{ or } p \text{ bad red. for } C\}]).
                    | Then
                    me N_0(f(P))  \lt \sum h_{D_k}(P) + O(1) = h_{D'}(P) + O(1)
                    | .
